org.incava.ijdk.lang

Class NullableObject<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.incava.ijdk.lang.NullableObject<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Int, Str

    public class NullableObject<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Extension to the Object class, wrapping a Java Object with additional methods. The referenced object can be null.
